ativistic\nplasmons, with their synchrotron spectra extending up to optical wavelengths.\nThis would render some of the V404 Cygni flares very similar to those of the\nwell-know microquasar GRS 1915+105\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2016 16:51:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-03"}
