ng field. On this basis the recipe is given for creating materials with a\ndesired refraction coefficient by embedding many small impedance particles into\na given material.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Jan 2016 01:25:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-12"}
