the above two\nhypotheses, but provides reasonable support for the intrinsic slowing down\nhypothesis. A significant fraction of the frequency independent delay during\nthe October 1997 event is indeed due to intrinsic slowing down of the Crab\nPulsar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Jan 2016 10:11:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
